labor_categories.labor_category: PDS Service - Control System Engineering and Design, Database Programming

raw_data.title: PDS Service - Control System Engineering and Design, Database Programming
raw_data.description: Consulting services for assistance with engineering of controls projects, product selection and application guidance, control shop drawing creation, programming, commissioning/functional-test assistance, and as-built drawing generation. Support of any aspect of control system solution development.
raw_data.required_certifications_or_licenses: Degree or Technical Certification from an accredited, applicable, Technologies program, or equivalent experience.

raw_data.title: PDS Service - Graphics Development
raw_data.description: Designs and implements custom site graphics for Delta Controls control system solutions using enteliVIZ Graphics, enteliVIZ Workflow Module and other developer tools. Provides Graphics Training, and Custom Web interfaces
raw_data.required_certifications_or_licenses: Degree or Technical Certification from an accredited, applicable, Technologies program, or equivalent experience.

raw_data.title: PDS Service – enteliWEB Tools Development
raw_data.description: Report customization and Firmware customization for Delta Controls control system solutions (enteliWEB). Manages software development design and implementation that may involve modification or maintenance of existing software solutions or development of new solutions, or consulting services to assist customer with their software development projects. Report customization service for creating, modifying, generating and scheduling report outputs for any aspect of reporting within the Delta Controls enteliWEB software.
raw_data.required_certifications_or_licenses: Degree or Technical Certification from an accredited, applicable, Technologies program, or equivalent experience.

raw_data.title: PDS Service - Integration Development
raw_data.description: Provides Application Software Development, Integration Drivers and API data connectivity for non-Delta Controls systems to connect to Delta systems.
raw_data.required_certifications_or_licenses: Degree or Technical Certification from an accredited, applicable, Technologies program, or equivalent experience.

raw_data.title: PDS Service – OEM Hardware, Firmware Development
raw_data.description: Designs and implements new hardware/firmware or modifications to existing Delta products to support functional requirements of OEM clients
